 <section id="sect-00007">
<title>Drug Calculation Methods and Rounding Rules</title>
<para id="para-00010">There are three general methods for drug calculation: basic formula method, ratio and proportion, and dimensional analysis. It is recommended that the learner use the method they are comfortable with. Additionally, some drugs require dosing based on weight and/or body surface area. These drugs require additional calculation. </para>
<section id="sect-00008">
  <title>Basic Formula Method</title>
<para id="para-00011">The basic formula method is the simplest of the drug calculation methods.</para>

<equation id="eq-00001">
  <m:math display="block">
    <m:mrow>
      <m:mtable>
        <m:mtr>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>D</m:mi></m:mtd>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>desired dose (dose ordered)</m:mtext></m:mtd>
        </m:mtr>
        <m:mtr>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mtext>___</m:mtext><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi></m:mtd>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>the drug on hand (what is available)</m:mtext></m:mtd>
        </m:mtr>
        <m:mtr>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>H</m:mi></m:mtd>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>the vehicle or volume of a drug form (tablet, capsule, liquid)</m:mtext></m:mtd>
        </m:mtr>
        <m:mtr>
          <m:mtd/>
          <m:mtd columnalign="left"><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>amount calculated to be administered to the patient</m:mtext></m:mtd>
        </m:mtr>
      </m:mtable>
    </m:mrow>
  </m:math>
</equation>

<list list-type="enumerated" id="list-00003">
  <item>Write the desired dose or the dose ordered.</item>
  <item>Write the drug dose on hand (available).</item>
  <item>Divide the desired dose by the dose on hand and multiply by the vehicle or volume of the drug form to get the amount calculated to be administered to the patient.</item>
</list>

<list list-type="bulleted" bullet-style="none" id="list-00004">
  <title>Example</title>
  <item>Order: Lisinopril 10 mg po bid</item>
  <item>Available: Lisinopril 2.5 mg</item>
  <item>How many tablets should the patient receive per dose?</item>
</list>

